cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.CY, cs.CR

This paper involves the analysis of social media data using Artificial Intelligence techniques from Natural Language Processing and Computer Vision fields. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also extensively analyzes textual and multimedia content, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the usefulness of the data for crisis management, which could place it in cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
